{
  "stem": "22734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was desperate because all I could do-- I sent a message to [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ruda. ?] We were supposed to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, you had 24 hours [? only. ?]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we met, and he said he'd do everything to-- to be able to go with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't tell anything to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know how he would arrange it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, I knew he would arrange it, deep in my heart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were terribly worried for my father, my mother and I, because he was still in jail in Prague.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Last time when he was in jail, he was 80 days in solitary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he-- you have to be exceptionally strong to do that with all the interviews-- if you want to call these interviews-- and if-- and the beating and the no food and the worries.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what happened to him-- what's happening to him now, we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And don't forget that by this time, when he first went to jail in December of '39, so-- the factory was confiscated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he lost everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- there was-- it was just gone, what was in it, lock, stock, and barrel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was-- we knew that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that somehow-- I don't know it-- but I don't really know, you know, if you ask me today, what-- where did the money come from that my mother bought-- was buying the food?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She must have had money somewhere because the bank accounts were closed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, that was the first thing the Germans did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the 15th of March, 1939, they matched in at 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By 8 o'clock, they were in Prague.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
